[Key Use Cases]1
　User calls out "let's talk" in a chat room with a bot
　The bot asks, "What would you like to see happen in this conversation?" I ask.
　Humans answer to it.
　Bots ask questions by selecting keywords from past human responses that they should dig into.
　The bot asks, at a time when the keywords are reasonably detailed, "What is it that you value?" and ask
　Bots ask questions about the relationship between two keywords with respect to keywords that have been fleshed out to some degree
　Ends when a human enters "bye-bye".

